#### Can I freeze the parathas? 

The dough can be refrigerated in an air-tight container for up to 3 days.
When using refrigerated dough, allow the dough to come to room temperature before rolling.
Cooked Parathas can be refrigerated for 3 to 4 days or frozen for longer shelf life. Reheat the Parathas on a stovetop griddle with a sprinkle of oil or ghee.

